## 🔧 Technical Requirements

### Minimum Requirements
- **Web Server**: Apache, Nginx, or any static file server
- **Browser Support**: Modern browsers (Chrome 60+, Firefox 55+, Safari 10+, Edge 16+)
- **No Database Required**: Static HTML/CSS/JS (database optional for advanced features)

### Recommended Enhancements
- **SSL Certificate**: For secure HTTPS connection
- **CDN**: CloudFlare or similar for global content delivery
- **Analytics**: Google Analytics or similar tracking
- **Backup System**: Regular automated backups
- **CMS Integration**: WordPress, Drupal, or custom CMS for easy content management

